  h1 30-day fully functional Free Trial
  .pull-right= image_tag 'secure-paypal-logo.png'
h4 NO credit card required for signup and first month!
br
h5
  = link_to "Sign up for FREE now", new_user_registration_path
  |  and only upgrade to a paid subscription plan if and when you need it.
  br
  |  All users start out on the FREE plan anyway!
  br
  | And remember: Paying Mantis often pays for itself! One recovered payment from an outstanding invoice can pay for your subscription!
