        li.plan-feature Every User starts off free! Only pay if you are happy with our service and only after month 1.
    .span3.plan
      .plan-name-bronze
        h2 Bronze
        span $30 (3 Months)
      ul
        li.plan-feature 16% Discount!
        li.plan-feature Get 16% discount by paying for 3 months up front, essentially $10 per month instead of $12! <strong>(Our Most Popular Plan)</strong>
    .span3.plan
      .plan-name-silver
        h2 Silver
        span $48 (6 Months)
      ul
        li.plan-feature 33% Discount!
        li.plan-feature Get 33% discount by paying for 6 months up front, essentially only paying $8 per month instead of $12!
    .span3.plan
      .plan-name-gold
        h2 Gold
        span $72 (1 Year)
      ul
        li.plan-feature 50% Discount!
        li.plan-feature Get 50% discount by paying for 1 year up front, essentially only paying $6 per month instead of $12!